{"tid":698751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「商品大王」 羅傑斯:投資北韓貨幣獲利前景極可觀","createTime":"2018-06-12T03:37:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T05:52:02.000Z","uid":14918,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"2929c1e3dd6007f2f02bb37c8082ed949101131e","tid":698751,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T03:37:59.000Z","msg":"「商品大王」 羅傑斯:投資北韓貨幣獲利前景極可觀<br />\n<br />\n2016年8月29日 國際財經 <br />\n<br />\n「商品大王」羅傑斯(Jim Rogers)表示，中國和俄羅斯的投資者正蜂擁闖入北韓市場。北韓百廢待興，獲利前景極其可觀。<br />\n<br />\n羅傑斯早前接受Real Vision TV訪問時指出，目前北韓就是「1981年的中國」。正如中國1978年對外開放，北韓也正處在開放的臨界點，此時正是絕佳的投資機會。他稱，「若我們現時投資在北韓貨幣上，未來某天將會變得富裕」。<br />\n<br />\n羅傑斯透露，一家中國集團已開始在北韓投資創建銀行。他本來也想投資這家集團，但他的律師卻稱因法律問題故不能投資。<br />\n<br />\n除了看好北韓以外，羅傑斯目前在津巴布韋也有投資，並且一直尋找機會在哈薩克和盧旺達進行投資。"},{"pid":"fc8ed5eef733dfddde97efd110b934f36e7708ed","tid":698751,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T03:58:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb692cd89a7b3ca9309f31ef526f229d058c92b0","tid":698751,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T04:00:07.000Z","msg":"玩命<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad7cb0508bfc166eeed360162f80571d56a41119","tid":698751,"uid":35930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T04:00:13.000Z","msg":"同買牛熊證一樣 DOUBLE OR NOTHING"},{"pid":"2be31014f47ce2ea49c07b57ff820993e132d93d","tid":698751,"uid":53429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T04:04:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ad232317cb4e36b28c8ab1ca0483b779040b378","tid":698751,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":